  "texts": [
    "In this study, we employ three commonly-adopted pre-trained open models: • LLaMA2-7B foot_0: The LLaMA2 series of LLM models (Touvron et al., 2023) developed by Meta.",
    "• Qwen2-7B foot_1.",
    "The Qwen2 series LLMs (Bai et al., 2023; Yang et al., 2024) from Alibaba, supporting long context lengths with strong performance on various benchmarks.",
    "• Mistral-7b-v0.",
    "Pre-trained base versions of the three models are selected for our experiments rather than their instruction-tuned variations for several reasons."
  ],
